5. Important Validators in WTForms
Validator---------------	Purpose
DataRequired()----------	Field cannot be empty
Email()-----------------	Valid email required
Length(min,max)---------    Limit characters
EqualTo()---------------	Password confirmation
NumberRange()-----------	Number limits
